{"tid":2320014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「對其直系親屬實施對等制裁」","createTime":"2020-12-10T12:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T12:58:23.000Z","uid":368978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d161d2c8706aa0e2a8bf61207fc40032422ead2b","tid":2320014,"uid":368978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:53:30.000Z","msg":"美國周一（12月7日）以香港問題為由，宣佈制裁14名中國全國人大副委員長。中國周四（12月10日）宣佈採取反制措施，決定對「在涉港問題上表現惡劣、負有主要責任的美國行政部門官員、國會人員、非政府組織人員及其直系親屬實施對等制裁」。同時，中方決定取消美方持外交護照人員臨時訪問香港和澳門的免簽待遇。<br />\n<br />\n梳史：<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-55256542.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-55256542.amp&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=529574f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-55256542.amp&h=dc855cb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-55256542.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n聽講美國都無制裁直系親屬，咁樣大返人轉頭唔驚架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d5913e69f0d14c27cebb19f0d1cbdb441e2422","tid":2320014,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"唔比你哋去中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98401f42942a1c0afaa1af8543e51a6fe493bb00","tid":2320014,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:56:00.000Z","msg":"制裁三代都唔覺可以改變到乜"},{"pid":"fc5832294289d0311a8fc6bcac8e4d5781578a28","tid":2320014,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:57:11.000Z","msg":"罰富豪及其家人以後唔準入劏房住"},{"pid":"5cd88252fa1480c67970084eba583cc7a0e0f0e4","tid":2320014,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"98401f42942a1c0afaa1af8543e51a6fe493bb00","tid":2320014,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12